text: B18 or B-18 may refer to: * Alton Bay Seaplane Base (FAA LID: B18) * B-18 Bolo, an American bomber aircraft by Douglas based on the Douglas DC-2 * B 18, a Swedish bomber aircraft made by SAAB. * B18 (New York City bus) serving Brooklyn * B18 road (Cyprus) * In chess, one of the ECO codes for the Caro- Kann Defence * HLA-B18, an HLA-B serotype * Honda B engine * The B-18 – 18' skiff designed by Julian Bethwaite * Volvo B18 engine
title: B18
